{"tid":2208820,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［分化L] 論手足","createTime":"2020-09-19T08:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T17:32:08.000Z","uid":317021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0f3b398b76cd0499898acb269017ed72eed5cb82","tid":2208820,"uid":317021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:10:44.000Z","msg":"唉，抗爭咁耐，見盡好多好假嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多都係買裝備，cosplay軍人，有啲仲着到成個防暴警察，速龍咁。遠睇真係嚇一下！我仲見唔少係public repost曬 抗爭page，但係私底下不停買警察用品，口吻好似dog咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知佢哋心底下係咪覺得警察好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔少急救熱誠者，明明自己只係普通急救牌，就着到成身反光衣，買曬EMT Paramedic袋 黐曬生命之星個logo。救命，呢啲頭銜係要有相應嘅牌先可以擺出黎，唔係俾你打飛機用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要po曬着住反光衣喺現場影背影，鬼唔知你係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以話我係分化，但係呢啲係我心底話，香港有嘅係言論自由。唔同意可以討論，但冇權叫我收聲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ba722acd22621f7d84fad80bb2140bf68cae7a","tid":2208820,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431d37cdaf1cb9fbf6742d325e0ae61fa45fa0b4","tid":2208820,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:30:18.000Z","msg":"可能唔少人都咁諗<br />\n但係連登唔可以講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0051d9c90a15022fcd92fd8fac694896c78331","tid":2208820,"uid":12186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:22:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50d70118a52d71e948adff5d619ea9277949eb0d","tid":2208820,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09: